        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35112654/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35112654/" class="">天朝帝国：停滞与倒退</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/60882783/" class=" " title="浮生可奈">浮生可奈</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="35112654">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">“中国前进的历史，是由亮点组成的历史。”</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-05-18 10:29</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                “中国前进的历史，是由亮点组成的历史。”
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







